---
title: Chipotle Salmon Bowls with Charred Corn-Tomato Salsa
description: Get delicious and flavourful salmon bowls in only 25 min! Succulent salmon is topped with sweet and smokey chipotle sauce to add a little flair to your dinner table, while a charred corn and tomato salsa takes things to the next level!
